history.content:
The Berkeley College of Engineering's Center for Access to Engineering Excellence (CAEE) opens its virtual doors for tutoring this week. Please see their calendar if you need support, and let them know if there are classes you would like to see added to their roster. Even though the center is run through the College of Engineering, other majors are welcome!
CAEE is looking for more tutors in EECS and CS. Please apply here if you're interested.
history.subject: Center for Access to Engineering Excellence (CAEE) Tutoring Now Available
